FAQs

1. What does my subscription include?

Your subscription gives you access to all vehicle auction data from the past three months, including images, inspection reports, and other essential details.

2. How often is the auction data updated?

We update our database daily to ensure you have the most accurate and up-to-date information.

3. Are there any additional charges apart from the subscription fee?

No, there are no hidden charges. Once you subscribe, you’ll have full access to the data as per your chosen plan.

4. Can I cancel my subscription at any time?

Yes, you can cancel your subscription at any time. However, access to auction data will be revoked at the end of your billing cycle.

5. Do you offer refunds?

We have a no-refund policy due to the nature of our service. Please review our plans carefully before subscribing.

6. Are there any discounts for long-term plans?

Yes, we occasionally offer discounts for annual subscriptions. Check our website or subscribe to our newsletter for updates.
